#: src/window.py:92
msgid "Theming"
msgstr "主题"

#: src/window.py:120
msgid ""
"After setting a color scheme, go to Gnome-Tweaks (or similar) and set "
"'Rewaita' as your Shell theme. It contains the same colors as the active "
"scheme for continuity\n"
"\n"
"Rewaita also does not style parts of apps like Gnome Builder and BlackBox "
"which have their own syntax highlighting system\n"
"\n"
"If you find a problem with any theme, would like to suggest another be "
"added, or want to submit your own to be included, please make an issue or a "
"pull request @ https://github.com/SwordPuffin/Rewaita"
msgstr ""
"设置颜色方案后，进入 Gnome-Tweaks（或类似工具），将“Rewaita”设置为您的 Shell "
"主题。它包含与当前使用的颜色方案相同的颜色以保持一致性。\n"
"\n"
"Rewaita 也不会为某些应用程序的部分界面设置样式，例如 Gnome Builder 和 "
"BlackBox，因为它们有自己的语法高亮系统。\n"
"\n"
"如果您发现任何主题有问题、想建议添加其他主题，或者希望提交自己的主题以供收"
"录，请在 @ https://github.com/SwordPuffin/Rewaita 提交 issue 或 pull "
"request。"

#: src/window.py:121
msgid ""
"**Rewaita will only style GTK3/4 applications; Any other UI libraries are "
"altogether NOT supported**"
msgstr "**Rewaita 仅适用于 GTK3/4 应用程序；其他 UI 库软件不受支持**"

